<Link id="l00496" /><CodeLine lineNumber="496"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// profile is already incorporated into the parent which is still useful and</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00504" /><CodeLine lineNumber="504"><Highlight kind="normal">      ProfileMap&#91;ChildProfile-&gt;getContext()&#93;.merge(&#42;ChildProfile);</Highlight></CodeLine>
